---
// Hero component — copy lives here so editing tone doesn't touch routing logic.
---

<section class="bg-dotgrid border-b border-line">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
    <p class="wordmark text-7xl md:text-9xl text-accent leading-none">Mika</p>

    <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink leading-tight">
        You prompt ChatGPT.<br/>
        <span class="text-accent">You call Mika.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">
        Una es conversación. La otra es infraestructura.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-base text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        Construida con tres certificaciones de Azure
        <span class="font-mono text-accent-ink">(AI-102 · AZ-204 · AZ-500)</span>
        como mapa, no como checklist. Audit-honest, multi-vendor, MCP-nativa.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          href="/docs"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 bg-accent text-white rounded-md font-semibold hover:bg-accent-ink transition-colors"
        >
          Lee la explicación completa
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="/posts"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 border border-line bg-paper text-ink-soft rounded-md font-semibold hover:border-accent hover:text-accent transition-colors"
        >
          Ver la serie
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
